    "description": "완전한 어둠 속에 있으면 사람은 무의식적으로 자신이 그 안에 혼자인지 생각에 사로 잡힙니다. 언젠가 불을 끄고 나면 등 뒤에서 사람이 아닌 누군가의 숨소리가 들릴 수도 있습니다. 어둠 속에서 일어나는 일은 빠르게 변화하고 있지만 빛이 악을 쫓아낼 수 있을까요?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >使用手电筒保护自己免受邪恶的伤害。</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008300/extras/05954ad18f48a9b224b1bdf88e7be7b5.poster.avif?t=1729710124\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008300/extras/05954ad18f48a9b224b1bdf88e7be7b5.webm?t=1729710124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008300/extras/05954ad18f48a9b224b1bdf88e7be7b5.mp4?t=1729710124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>就在不久前，这里还是你的家，但现在情况有变......有东西从墙后冒出来，它们躲在黑暗中，它们在跟踪你。但他们是真的存在，还是只是你的精神错乱？<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >事件瞬息万变！</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008300/extras/66e38d8f6e3c2fef18f76373c51caebb.poster.avif?t=1729710124\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008300/extras/66e38d8f6e3c2fef18f76373c51caebb.webm?t=1729710124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008300/extras/66e38d8f6e3c2fef18f76373c51caebb.mp4?t=1729710124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>他们正在改变。从现在起，这里就是他们的居所，他们正在等待黑暗降临，来对付你。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你能活下去吗？</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008300/extras/874579d8223ec8495acfe4e118392a89.poster.avif?t=1729710124\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008300/extras/874579d8223ec8495acfe4e118392a89.webm?t=1729710124\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008300/extras/874579d8223ec8495acfe4e118392a89.mp4?t=1729710124\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>使用找到的物品，在躲避和吓跑怪物的同时完成任务。努力保卫自己的家园！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>紧张刺激的恐怖游戏：您将体验到恐惧和惊喜的时刻。<br></li><li>使用手电筒：生物害怕光线。<br></li><li>各种任务：寻找和使用物品来完成任务，探索不断变化的住所。<br></li><li>令人讨厌的敌人：躲避和抵挡潜伏在黑暗中的邪恶生物的攻击。<br></li><li>不断变化的地点：在入侵生物的影响下，你的住所会逐渐发生变化。<br></li><li>故事情节：有多个结局。</li></ul><br>准备好沉浸在恐怖和紧张的氛围中吧，在这里，你迈出的每一步都可能是最后一步。你的住所已成为与邪恶斗争的竞技场。您能生存下来并保持理智吗？",
